Thanks a ton, here is the page: <https://www.brandify.com/product/local-pages>. It's the two CTAs in the hero.

This is my script:

```&lt;script&gt;

$(window).on('load resize', function() { 
       //create array for each element that needs checked and resized
        var ctaHeights = [];
        //loop through the container elements
        var $ctaButtons = $('.jumbo-lp-9-hero .cta_button');
         $ctaButtons.each(function() {
            //get element's height
            var ctaHeight = $(this).height();
            //add heights to array
            ctaHeights.push(ctaHeight);
        });
        //get tallest height
        var tallestCTA = Math.max.apply(Math, ctaHeights);

        //set height to tallest height
        $ctaButtons.css('height', tallestCTA + 'px');
});
&lt;/script&gt;```

